data.description: Fabulous Stucco 6 bed 3.5 bath 3 car on corner lot.  Tiled entry foyer invites you to dining (currently office) or living room.  Open concept living room to breakfast nook and kitchen with fireplace. Garage enters to laundry room, 1/2 bath, and kitchen.  Bedroom behind kitchen can be used for office and currently has a glass door and doggie door access to back yard.   Kitchen offers breakfast nook for kiddos or guests.  Upstairs you will find primary suite with 5 pc. bath, 3 other bedrooms and full bath.  Downstairs is VERY large family room with wet bar, bedroom and full bathroom.  This area offers a Community Center with pool, exercise equip. +, plenty of walking paths and is close to EVERYTHING!  The home offers a warm aesthetic, semi-open concept, plenty of space with a fantastic layout.  You will not want to miss this one.
